    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331030/extras/b30bfd3686eba5f00fce3fb1571676a2.avif?t=1740422254\" width=800 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demo of Annie's School Trip is about a young student called Annie. She has a field trip to go along with the other students fom her school. While she was exploring the new area she ends up doing something wrong... Now a big threat is coming for her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331030/extras/021ac61fae615cff9652dc9ad21af30a.avif?t=1740422254\" width=800 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo is a sidescroller platformer horror game. You need to get to the other side of the screen avoiding the obstacles just like the main game. There's also has some comedy and dark humor stuff in it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demo contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some levels to go through, jumping over the holes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >comedy and dark humor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >scary situations.</p></li></ul>",
